msg: Note that using SSLProtocol="TLSv1.1,TLSv1.2" requires native 1.1.32 or later.
Running with 1.1.31 is OK as long as the new values are not used in configuration.
It is merge of r1632975 from tomcat/trunk.

author: kkolinko
msg: Note that using SSLProtocol="TLSv1.1,TLSv1.2" requires native 1.1.32 or later.
Running with 1.1.31 is OK as long as the new values or the value "all" (default) are not used in configuration.
Using "TLSv1.1" with Tomcat Native 1.1.31 results in
Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Invalid Server SSL Protocol (error:00000000:lib(0):func(0):reason(0))
